{"lemma":"جَنَباتِ","slug":"جَنَباتِ","root":"ج.ن.ب","root_slug":"ج-ن-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ن-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6411","n6412","n6419","n6420","n6421"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6411","headword_ar":"جَنَبَهُ","root":"jnb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He broke his side:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he hit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurt, his side."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [The aor. of the verb in this sense is probably"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the inf. n., accord. to the TK, is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janobN","text_ar":"جَنْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He led him by his side;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, * Msb, K;) namely, a horse (S, A, Msb, TA) or the like, (S, A,) and a captive. (S, TA.) In this sense, its aor. is"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Msb, TA,) and the inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janabN","text_ar":"جَنَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majonabN","text_ar":"مَجْنَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TawoEu Aljanabi","text_ar":"طَوْعُ الجَنَبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janabN .jinaAbN","text_ar":"جَنَبٌ .جِنَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"which is forbidden (S, A, TA) in a trad., [in which it is said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA jalaba walaA janaba","text_ar":"لَا جَلَبَ وَلَا جَنَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (A, TA) relating to horse-racing and to [the collecting of] the poor-rate, (TA,) means [in the former case]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man's leading, by the side of a horse that he rides in a race, another horse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without a rider,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and when the horse that he rides has become languid and weak,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when he fears that he will not outstrip upon it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when he draws near to the goal,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"transferring himself to the other,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order that he may outstrip:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) and in relation to the poorrate, it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the collector's alighting in the most remote of the places whence the portion appointed for the poor-rate is to be collected, and then ordering that the camels or the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that constitute that portion"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shall be led to him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going of the owner of the property to a distance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"aside,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"out of the way,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with his property, so that the collector is obliged to go to a distance in quest of it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K. See more in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jlb","text_ar":"جلب"},{"kind":"text","text":", first paragraph.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He placed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put, at a distance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he put,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sent, away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"far away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"far off,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he removed far away, alienated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"estranged, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as though he put him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, aside,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as though he walked aside;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jAnbhu","text_ar":"جانبهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He pushed, thrust,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drove, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, away, aside,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to a distance."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janabahu Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"جَنَبَهُ الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, *) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~ar~a","text_ar":"الشَّرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, Zj, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Msb, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jn~bhu","text_ar":"جنّبهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, Zj, S, A, Msb, K,) but this has an intensive signification; (Msb;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajnbhu","text_ar":"اجنبهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Fr, Zj, A, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put aside,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he warded off, from him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he removed from him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"removed far from him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, *) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, Zj, A, Msb.) It is said in the Kur [xiv. 38],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA@jonuboniY wabaniY~a A^ano naEobuda AlA^aSonaAma","text_ar":"وَا@جْنُبْنِى وَبَنِىَّ اَنْ نَعْبُدَ الاَصْنَامَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And put Thou away from me and my sons our worshipping of idols"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S,) or, accord. to one reading, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA^ajoniboniY","text_ar":"وَاَجْنِبْنِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He yearned towards, longed for,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desired, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janaba bihi","text_ar":"جَنَبَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"page_break","n":465},{"kind":"text","text":"aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went aside, apart, out of the way, to a distance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"far away, with him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janabahu","text_ar":"جَنَبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in a sense explained above,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he placed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put, at a distance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he put,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sent, away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"far away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"far off, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janaba fiY baniY fulaAnK","text_ar":"جَنَبَ فِى بَنِى فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, *) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janaAbapN","text_ar":"جَنَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tjn~b","text_ar":"تجنّب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (so, app., in the TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He alighted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"descended and abode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"settled, as a stranger, among the sons of such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, * TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"niEoma Alqawomu humo lijaAri AljanaAbapi","text_ar":"نِعْمَ القَوْمُ هُمْ لِجَارِ الجَنَابَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Excellent are the people, they,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the neighbour who is a stranger."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junubN","text_ar":"جُنُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA","text_ar":"لَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHoriman~iY Eano janaAbapK","text_ar":"تَحْرِمَنِّى عَنْ جَنَابَةٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Do not thou by any means refuse me because of being remote"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in respect of relationship."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janaAbapN","text_ar":"جَنَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"mentioned below as a subst.] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janabati Alr~iyHu","text_ar":"جَنَبَتِ الرِّيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junuwbN","text_ar":"جُنُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajnbt","text_ar":"اجنبت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The wind was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"januwb","text_ar":"جَنُوب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"south,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"southerly"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it blew in the direction of the wind thus called:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) or the former, (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janibat","text_ar":"جَنِبَت"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the wind changed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"veered, so as to become"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"januwb","text_ar":"جَنُوب"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) ―         -b4-  [And hence, (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"januwbN","text_ar":"جَنُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janaba A_ilayohi","text_ar":"جَنَبَ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAar, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY liqaAy^ihi","text_ar":"اـِلَى لِقَايِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janiba","text_ar":"جَنِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Th, K;) [inf. n., app.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janobN","text_ar":"جَنْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for the verb is said in the K to be like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSara","text_ar":"نَصَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samiEa","text_ar":"سَمِعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, disquieted by vehement desire to see him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to meet him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janiba","text_ar":"جَنِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janabN","text_ar":"جَنَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"limped,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"halted, by reason of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pain in"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his side:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he had an affection resembling"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaloE","text_ar":"ظَلْع"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"limping,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"halting"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but not the same as this:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and, (K,) or accord. to As, (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his lungs clave to his side by reason of vehement thirst:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or, accord. to the Arabs of the desert, as ISk says,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became bent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contorted, by reason of vehemence of thirst:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had a pain in his side from vehemence of thirst."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) The epithet is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janibN","text_ar":"جَنِبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; which is applied by Dhu-r-Rummeh to an ass. (S, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jnbt Ald~alowu","text_ar":"جنبت الدَّلْوُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janibat","text_ar":"جَنِبَت"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The bucket inclined to one side in consequence of the breaking of one or two of the thongs attacking it to the cross-bars."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janiba","text_ar":"جَنِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"januba","text_ar":"جَنُبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janaba","text_ar":"جَنَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"are"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajonaba","text_ar":"اَجْنَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a sense explained below: see 4.       -A5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juniba","text_ar":"جُنِبَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He had,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became affected by, the disease termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAtu Aljanobi","text_ar":"ذَاتُ الجَنْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleurisy"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, Mgh, Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he had a complaint of his side."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)       -A6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junibuwA","text_ar":"جُنِبُوا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They were,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, affected by the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"south,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"southerly, wind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junuwb","text_ar":"جُنُوب"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, A, K.) And also, [in allusion to the fertilizing effect attributed to the wind so called,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They were,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, affected by that wind in their cattle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","A","Msb","TA","Fr","Zj","IAar","Mgh"]},{"entry_id":"n6412","headword_ar":"جنّبهُ","root":"jnb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 1: ―         -b2-  and see also 3.       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jnb~","text_ar":"جنبّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tajoniybN","text_ar":"تَجْنِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did not send the stallion-camel among his she-camels, nor the ram or he-goat among his ewes or she-goats."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jn~b Alqawomu","text_ar":"جنّب القَوْمُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The milk of the people's camels became little:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the people's milk ceased;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became little:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the people's camels had no milk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jn~b","text_ar":"جنّب"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a man,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his camels had no milk, nor had his sheep or goats."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmu","text_ar":"عَامُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tajoniybK","text_ar":"تَجْنِيبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A year of little,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"no, milk"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jn~bt AlA^ibilu","text_ar":"جنّبت الاِبِلُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camels, with the exception of one or two, brought forth no young."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, TA.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camels did not conceive, so as to have milk."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tajoniybN","text_ar":"تَجْنِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as an inf. n. of which the verb, if it have one in any of the following senses, is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jun~iba","text_ar":"جُنِّبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bending,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"curving, and tension"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the sinews"},{"kind":"text","text":"] ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tawotiyrN","text_ar":"تَوْتِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the hind leg of a horse;"},{"kind":"text","text":"which is a quality approved: (S, K:) or, accord. to AO,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a turning aside of his fore legs in raising them and putting them down:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but accord. to As, it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the kind legs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHoniybN","text_ar":"تَحْنِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is in the back-bone and in the fore legs. (TA.) [See also 2 in art"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hnb","text_ar":"حنب"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mujan~abN","text_ar":"مُجَنَّبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n6419","headword_ar":"جَنْبَةٌ","root":"jnb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janobN","text_ar":"جَنْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places: ―         -b2-  and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAnibN","text_ar":"جَانِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Retirement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"secession, from others:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) and in a trad., in which it is enjoined, used as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retirement from women; avoiding the sitting by them, and the approaching the place that they occupy."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN *uw janobapK","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ ذُو جَنْبَةٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man of retirement."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nazala janobapF","text_ar":"نَزَلَ جَنْبَةً"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He alighted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"descended and abode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"settled, in a place aside,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"apart."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEada janobapF","text_ar":"قَعَدَ جَنْبَةً"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sat apart,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retired from others."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b4-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state of being a stranger;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janaAbapN","text_ar":"جَنَابَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K. [Both are there mentioned as simple substs.; but the latter is an inf. n.: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janaba fiY baniY fulaAnK","text_ar":"جَنَبَ فِى بَنِى فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and what next follows it: and see also 4.]) Both also signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Remoteness in respect of relationship."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  Also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janobapN","text_ar":"جَنْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece of skin from the side of a camel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K, *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which is made a kind of milking vessel"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eulobap","text_ar":"عُلْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"), (S, L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"larger than the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miEolaq","text_ar":"مِعْلَق"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but smaller than the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawobap","text_ar":"جَوْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.)       -A3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Every kind of plant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"page_break","n":467},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"every kind of tree in general,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that produces"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"new leaves such as are termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabol","text_ar":"رَبْل"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the season of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sayof","text_ar":"صَيْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which may mean either"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"summer"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spring"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"every kind of plant that produces leaves in that season without rain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or a name given to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"many plants, all of them"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euruwq","text_ar":"عُرُوق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[perhaps meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling roots,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"straggling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spreading like roots"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; so called because"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"less than large trees and higher than those that have no root-stock"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aruwmap","text_ar":"اَرُومَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the earth; comprising the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSiY~","text_ar":"نَصِىّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sil~iyaAn","text_ar":"صِلِّيَان"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamaAT","text_ar":"حَمَاط"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"makor","text_ar":"مَكْر"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"H*r","text_ar":"حذر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[so in the TA, but I do not find it elsewhere, and think it may be a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hazor","text_ar":"حَزْر"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hazorap","text_ar":"حَزْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the name of a certain sour tree) is probably the n. un.,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dahomaA='","text_ar":"دَهْمَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which are smaller than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ajar","text_ar":"شَجَر"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and superior to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buquwl","text_ar":"بُقُول"},{"kind":"text","text":": all this has been heard from the Arabs: (T, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"green and fresh"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sl~yAn","text_ar":"صلّيان"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a kind"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baqol","text_ar":"بَقْل"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ajar","text_ar":"شَجَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (AHn, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the TA"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"whmA","text_ar":"وهما"},{"kind":"text","text":", but this is evidently a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wahiYa","text_ar":"وَهِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the kind of which the root remains in the winter while the branches perish:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage of which the root is deep in the earth; such as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSiY~","text_ar":"نَصِىّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sil~iyaAn","text_ar":"صِلِّيَان"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaDirN","text_ar":"خَضِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S","L","T","AHn"]},{"entry_id":"n6420","headword_ar":"جَنَبَةٌ","root":"jnb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janobN","text_ar":"جَنْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places: ―         -b2-  and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAnibN","text_ar":"جَانِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n6421","headword_ar":"جُنَبَةٌ","root":"jnb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing from which one retires,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"withdraws himself, to a distance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"far away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"far off; from which one stands,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"keeps, aloof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}